{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Dynamic programming language（动态编程语言）","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Dynamic_programming_language","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>动态编程语言</strong>是指可在运行阶段时执行那些在编译阶段执行的操作的编程语言。比如，在 JavaScript 中，我们可以在程序运行时改变变量的类型，或者为一个对象增加一个新属性或者方法。</p>\n<p>这正好与静态编程语言相反，在静态编程语言的运行阶段，一般是无法执行这些改变的。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 尽管静态/动态编程语言和 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Dynamic_typing\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">静态/动态类型 (en-US)</a>有一定的联系，但是两者并不是同义词。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_knowledge","title":"General knowledge","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a title=\"Dynamic programming language\" href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_programming_language\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Dynamic programming language</a> on Wikipedia</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"动态编程语言是指可在运行阶段时执行那些在编译阶段执行的操作的编程语言。比如，在 JavaScript 中，我们可以在程序运行时改变变量的类型，或者为一个对象增加一个新属性或者方法。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Lenguaje de programación dinámico","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Langage de programmation dynamique","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Dynamic programming language (動的プログラミング言語)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"동적 프로그래밍 언어","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Linguagem de programação dinâmica","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Динамический язык программирования","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/dynamic_programming_language","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/dynamic_programming_